to]]<ref>{{cite news |title=North Cotabato reports 1st Covid-19 positive case |url=https://www.pna.gov.ph/articles/1098930 |accessdate=April 7, 2020 |agency=Philippine News Agency |date=April 7, 2020}}</ref>\n**''[[General Santos]]''<ref name=\"gensan\">{{cite news |title=General Santos City reports first COVID-19 case |url=https://www.cnnphilippines.com/regional/2020/4/8/general-santos-city-covid-19.html |accessdate=April 8, 2020 |work=CNN Philippines |date=April 8, 2020}}</ref>\n**[[South Cotabato]]<ref name=\"PNAGovPH-CovidSouthCotabato\">{{cite news |last1=Osano |first1=Roel |title=South Cotabato confirms 1st positive Covid-19 case |url=https://www.pna.gov.ph/articles/1098326 |accessdate=March 31, 2020 |work=Philippine News Agency |date=March 31, 2020 |language=en}}</ref>\n**[[Sultan Kudarat]]<ref>{{cite news |title=With confirmed COVID-19 case, Sultan Kudarat to impose lockdown, curfew |url=https://www.mindanews.com/top-stories/2020/03/with-confirmed-covid-19-case-sultan-kudarat-to-impose-lockdown-curfew/ |accessdate=March 30, 2020 |work=MindaNews |date=March 27, 2020}}</ref>\n*[[Caraga]] (Region XIII)\n**''[[Butuan]]''{{refn|group=note|name=Butuan cases|Sole case admitted to the Caraga Regional Hospital in [[Surigao City]]<ref>{{cite news|url=https://cnnphilippines.com/regional/2020/4/6/caraga-all-regions-covid-19-cases.html|title=Caraga reports first COVID-19 case|work=CNN Philippines|date=April 6, 2020|accessdate=April 6, 2020}}</ref><ref name=\"caraganolonger\">{{cite news |last1=Panganiban |first1=Chris |title=Caraga region no longer COVID-19 free |url=https://www.mindanews.com/top-stories/2020/04/caraga-region-no-longer-covid-19-free/ |accessdate=April 7, 2020 |work=MindaNews |date=April 6, 2020}}</ref>}}\n**[[Surigao del Norte]]{{refn|group=note|name=Surigao del Norte cases|Sole case imported from Butuan<ref name=\"caraganolonger\"/>}}\n*[[Bangsamoro]] (BARMM)\n**''[[Cotabato City]]''<ref name=\"PIAGovPH-CovidCotabatoCity\">{{cite news |title=Cotabato Ci